  <title>Point soil data: Layer main descriptions</title>
  <abstract>It contains the point soil data layer main description by certain observable characteristics. The other parts of the layer data are in the Gis data: &quot;Point soil data: Matrix colour&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Redoximorphic&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Layer Coarse fragments&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Layer Artefacts&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Layer Structure&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Layer Coatings and bridges&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Cracks&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Layer Carbonates&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Layer Secondary carbonates&quot;; &quot;Point soil data: Layer Gypsum&quot;; &quot;Point soil data:Layer Secondary silica&quot;; &quot;Point soil data:Layer Human alterations&quot;.  It is associated/linked to &quot;Point soil data: General&quot;</abstract>
